					<h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-purple-400 mb-2">ðŸ”’ Zone Currently Locked</h2>
					<p class="text-gray-400">Log 10 total NUTs to unlock Spirit features</p>
					<div class="mt-3">
						<div class="bg-black/30 rounded-full h-4 overflow-hidden">
